thread.title: Customer

author: Customer
title: Customer
text: I was able to reserve a storage space online the night before I needed the storage, which was a very big plus for my situation! The next morning checking in with Kathy was a very easy & quick process. Customer service was great all throughout my interaction with Kathy, none of my questions went unanswered. I love that there is a gate code to enter & leave the property. They basically have any packing supplies you may need, which was great. You will need to bring your own lock or purchase one from them. I wasn't aware of that before going up there but it was no big deal because they had some available for purchase.
